# Code ownership for infektyd/minni.
#
# Syntax: https://docs.github.com/articles/about-code-owners
# Last matching pattern wins. @infektyd is the repo owner and the catch-all
# reviewer; per-surface lines exist so ownership stays explicit as the project
# grows additional maintainers.

# Catch-all: everything is owned by the repo owner unless overridden below.
*                       @infektyd

# Python engine + daemon.
/engine/                @infektyd

# Multi-host TypeScript plugin.
/plugins/               @infektyd

# Docs, contracts, and top-level project surface.
/docs/                  @infektyd
/README.md              @infektyd
/AGENTS.md              @infektyd

# Build/CI/ownership tooling and git hooks.
/.github/               @infektyd
/.githooks/             @infektyd
/Makefile               @infektyd
